translate indonesian ep5_milf_72_893c131c:
    # mc "Damn, I'm late. It's night outside..."
    mc "Sial, aku terlambat. Di luar sudah malam..."

translate indonesian ep5_milf_72_5b2cf12d:
    # mc "I hope my plan has at least partially come to fruition."
    mc "Kuharap rencanaku setidaknya sebagian berhasil."

translate indonesian ep5_milf_72_8e997fb4:
    # mc "Or maybe nothing happened at all."
    mc "Atau mungkin tidak terjadi apa-apa sama sekali."

translate indonesian ep5_milf_72_2_224855b0:
    # mc "It's suspiciously quiet...."
    mc "Sunyi mencurigakan...."

translate indonesian ep5_milf_72_2_7305b670:
    # mc "Too quiet..."
    mc "Terlalu sunyi..."

translate indonesian ep5_milf_72_2_91b15db8:
    # mc "Why am I panicking? Maybe Mary has sent the officer home and gone to bed."
    mc "Kenapa aku panik? Mungkin Mary sudah menyuruh petugas itu pulang dan pergi tidur."

translate indonesian ep5_milf_72_2_38cf25a7:
    # mc "And my brother, judging by everything, hasn't showed up or maybe someone told him he was wrong."
    mc "Dan kakakku, dilihat dari semuanya, belum muncul atau mungkin seseorang memberitahunya bahwa dia salah."

translate indonesian ep5_milf_72_2_ca23022a:
    # mc "Otherwise I can't... and I don't want to explain this damn silence."
    mc "Kalau tidak, aku tidak bisa... dan tidak ingin menjelaskan kesunyian sialan ini."

translate indonesian ep5_milf_72_2_421a0fd3:
    # mc "Even if I think about it..."
    mc "Kalaupun kupikirkan..."

translate indonesian ep5_milf_72_2_479928e1:
    # mc "No, no, I don't want to even think about that."
    mc "Tidak, tidak, aku bahkan tidak mau memikirkan itu."

translate indonesian ep5_milf_72_2_eb63ae67:
    # mc "But... alright, alright! I'll give it a thought!"
    mc "Tapi... baiklah, baiklah! Aku akan memikirkannya!"

translate indonesian ep5_milf_72_2_90336e56:
    # mc "Even if I assume the worst case scenario where my brother found Mary and officer dining together and that officer didn't have time to hide in the toilet or decided not to hide... there's a chance someone was killed."
    mc "Bahkan kalau kuasumsikan skenario terburuk, kakakku menemukan Mary dan petugas itu sedang makan malam bersama, lalu petugas itu tidak sempat bersembunyi di toilet atau memutuskan untuk tidak bersembunyi... ada kemungkinan seseorang terbunuh."

translate indonesian ep5_milf_72_2_883a76cb:
    # mc "If the officer had defended himself and shot my brother, there would have been a bunch of cops crowding the place long ago, the murder would have been processed as self-defence, and I would have received a text message from Mary asking me to come to the police station."
    mc "Kalau petugas itu membela diri dan menembak kakakku, pasti sudah ada banyak polisi memenuhi tempat ini sejak tadi, pembunuhan itu akan diproses sebagai pembelaan diri, dan aku akan menerima pesan dari Mary yang memintaku datang ke kantor polisi."

translate indonesian ep5_milf_72_2_f2103669:
    # mc "Had my brother topped the officer, I would have received a message from him."
    mc "Kalau kakakku menghabisi petugas itu, aku pasti menerima pesan darinya."

translate indonesian ep5_milf_72_2_f9467a9e:
    # mc "As much as I disapprove of what he did, I'm the only one he trusts 146%%."
    mc "Meskipun aku tidak setuju dengan perbuatannya, akulah satu-satunya orang yang dia percayai 146%%."

translate indonesian ep5_milf_72_2_a5dc9897:
    # mc "All in all, it means no one was killed in here..."
    mc "Kesimpulannya, itu berarti tidak ada yang terbunuh di sini..."

translate indonesian ep5_milf_72_2_bac23122:
    # mc "Well, I must say it's a relief."
    mc "Yah, harus kuakui itu melegakan."

translate indonesian ep5_milf_72_2_21871263:
    # mc "I think I should go change before checking on Mary."
    mc "Kurasa aku harus ganti pakaian sebelum mengecek keadaan Mary."

translate indonesian strings:
    old "Переодеться в повседневную одежду у себя в комнате."
    new "Ganti ke pakaian biasa di kamarmu"
